title: Phande Poriya Boga Kande Re
subTitle: A light-hearted wedding turns tense when buried family rivalries threaten to explode, testing the resolve of a newly arrived son-in-law.

title: Cocktail
subTitle: When Kishaloy shifts to Kolkata and looks for a place to live, he is rejected by most landlords as he is a bachelor. When he finally manages to find a home, he lies about his marital status.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati realises Narayan's deceit. She confronts him to declare his true identity and refuses to marry. Mainadevi becomes anxious when Parvati transforms into Goddess Adishakti.

title: Ichchhamoyee Maa
subTitle: Kanhai is a simple man who has a smaller income compared to his brother, Balai, the head priest of their temple. When Kanhai's wife gets jealous of his brother's income, the goddess blesses them.

title: Tumi Ele Tai
subTitle: Akash, a headstrong man, shares a special bond with his grandfather. When a dejected Arundhati faces failure in her relationships, Akash and his grandfather support her and try to alleviate her pain.

title: Paribar
subTitle: Rahul ventures into the smuggling business and lands in trouble. However, his brother Sagar takes the blame to protect him and their family.

title: Sasur Bari Zindabad
subTitle: While running away from an arranged marriage, Rupa meets Sonu, a mechanic who changes her life forever.

title: Manik
subTitle: Samir Mitra impersonates his deceased friend to get a job. Later, when he falls in love with his employer's daughter and mutual relations meet, his identity is questioned.

title: Awara
subTitle: Surya falls in love with a girl and follows her to Kolkata, where she stays with her rowdy elder brother. Later, he decides to rescue her when he discovers that a gangster wants to marry her forcibly.

title: Prem Amar
subTitle: A young man falls in love with his new neighbour. However, his life takes a turn for the worse when he learns that she is betrothed to another man.

title: Prem Amar
subTitle: A young man falls in love with his new neighbour. However, his life takes a turn for the worse when he learns that she is betrothed to another man.

title: Mahapith Tarapith
subTitle: Sameer Roy, a lawyer, is a devotee of Tara Maa while his friend, Ajay, does not believe in God. When Ajay's son falls sick, Sameer believes that only Tara Maa can save him.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: After learning about Parvati's true identity, Mainadevi realises her mistake. Ganga implores Mainadevi to grant permission for the wedding of Lord Shiva and Parvati.

title: Chaalbaaz
subTitle: Anju endures mistreatment at home, whereas her long-separated twin Manju boldly navigates life's challenges. By some quirk of fate, they end up trading places, and their worlds erupt in chaos.

title: Bhalobasa Bhalobasa
subTitle: A girl falls in love with a boy, the son of a famous deceased singer. However, the couple faces many obstacles when the girl's father decides to get her married to another man.

title: Sakhi Tumi Kar
subTitle: Sagar, a youngster, falls in love with Asim Dutta's daughter, Sakhi. As he is a dominant landlord in their village, he gets Sagar arrested on false charges of murder to keep him away from Sakhi.

title: Sneher Protidan
subTitle: Mohan loves his brothers a lot and tries to ensure they do well in life. However, all of them fall prey to a misunderstanding, which risks their bond.

title: Le Halua Le
subTitle: Sonali moves to the city to earn money and repay her debts to her landlord. She fakes a marriage with Suvojeet, a struggling artist, in order to get low-priced accommodation.

title: Annadata
subTitle: Sankar's life changes when he gets taken in by a rich businessman. Years later, an opportunity arises for him to prove his loyalty to his adopted family.

title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Challenge 2
subTitle: ACP Abhiraj Roy, who believes his father is dead, accepts the challenge to catch a dangerous mobster. He soon discovers the source of corruption in the political nexus and decides to end it.

title: Chopper
subTitle: Rajat and Rina's love blossoms amidst the struggles of the working class. However, their relationship is tested when they face political turmoil, social injustice and the harsh realities of life.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: After learning that Mainadevi grants permission for the wedding, Tarakasura becomes enraged. However, He devises a plan to thwart the marriage.

title: Goopy Bagha Phire Elo
subTitle: Granted three wishes by a benign Goblin king Goopy and Bagha receive food clothes magic slippers and the power to hold people spellbound with music.

title: Dadar Aadesh
subTitle: A devoted family man's world shatters when betrayal leads to tragedy, leaving loved ones divided and struggling to rebuild trust amidst deep-seated resentment.

title: Sindurer Adhikar
subTitle: Misunderstandings cause Prijay and Susmita's marriage to fall apart and she moves to her brother Prakash's house. Prijay's illness, however, makes her rethink her decision.

title: Chore Chore Mastuto Bhai
subTitle: John is hired by Nagraj to steal a diamond but ends up betraying him, inviting his ire. Before Nagraj's henchman kills John, he gives the diamond to a taxi driver for safekeeping.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: Two families of opposing faiths are in a long-standing rivalry over land and past wounds. However, one man vows to reunite them by disguising himself as a Hindu person.

title: Pratibad
subTitle: A fierce fighter against injustice strives to help his middle-class family make ends meet. His dedication lands him a job as a police officer, where he tackles large-scale problems with determination.

title: Sud Asol
subTitle: A determined police officer seeks justice from a man who destroyed his father's life several years ago.
